264
00:15:12,721 --> 00:15:14,681
lots of money.

265
00:15:14,723 --> 00:15:17,309
I mean boatloads of money, Jill.

266
00:15:17,351 --> 00:15:20,562
What do you know
about being an executive?

267
00:15:20,604 --> 00:15:21,939
You're a flier, Spence.

268
00:15:21,980 --> 00:15:23,524
No, honey.

269
00:15:23,565 --> 00:15:26,276
What I am
is a true American hero.

